{"tid":1447042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論求置頂] 抗爭戰術/策略研討整合區","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:38.000Z","uid":2617,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"661a4fc4c878380e4a8ebe2c6f1f8785bd965073","tid":1447042,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"呢個post首先有兩點希望大家留意：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>1. 保持心平氣和</ins></span></span><br />\n見到有少少唔同睇法既巴絲 唔好一開波就屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論係前線定冷軍都好 大家都係反共同路人<br />\n互相了解下對方點諗 對運動一定係有利無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>2. 定期整合各英雄意見</ins></span></span><br />\n我會keep住幫大家寫一個summary<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等大家唔駛追晒成個post咁辛苦 (好似平時press con mark重點咁)<br />\n<br />\n呢到我拋磚幾點睇下大家有咩意見<br />\n或者大家可以就其他方向討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>1. 警犬轉陣</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n(a) 瘋狂放一輪tear gas, 然後就有速龍+防暴快速攻擊, 好多手足同時一齊跑走, 但次次都有人走唔切中伏<br />\n(b) 有狗扮示威者裝束/匿係架車到, 然後衝出黎拉人<br />\n(c) D狗已經當地鐵站係戰場, 連轉場都有難度 <br />\n(好似岩岩2215係鰂魚涌都已經圍住個站唔比你出)<br />\n<br />\nc我未諗到, b既文宣手足同大家一定幫到手<br />\n已經有晒圖證明班撚樣扮手足拉示威者<br />\n一定要煲大呢單野<br />\n咩放火扔磚全撚部係警犬做<br />\n加埋今晚有絲打被射盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要咬住唔放咁追究<br />\n<br />\n主要想講一講a<br />\n而家好多時我地圍警署 都係瘋狂扔野入狗屋<br />\n但係如果唔係扔炸彈入去既話 除左爆下玻璃之外<br />\n未見到有咩效果 似乎係咁用laser射已經夠做<br />\n留定彈藥 等佢地出黎先扔同攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當佢地放完彈衝出黎個陣 好多都已經係全速前進捉人<br />\n而我地就好被動 等佢地出黎就喪跑走 結果次次有手足被捕/受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果等佢地出黎 有人就瘋狂扔野(已經有人會做 但似乎唔夠) <br />\n佢地點都要避一避 冇咁容易全速 </span></span><br />\n變相有D緩衝 真係要撤退都容易D<br />\n<br />\n再進一步 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有一大班人係夠勇 就算佢地出黎唔退既話<br />\n佢地得百幾個 唔係幾覺得佢地仲夠膽全速衝 </span></span><br />\n當然呢個就涉及反攻既問題 唔知道有幾多人有呢個決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(可以參考番2016旺角事件 呢段片既頭一part:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aGgZw1RJc_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaGgZw1RJc_0&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=a30c8034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aGgZw1RJc_0</a> )<br />\n夠人既話 當然搏得過!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>2. 整體策略</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n承上 如果未夠人肯做轉守為攻既話<br />\n咁而家堵路+圍狗屋+佢出黎我地走佬既策略<br />\n就有轉變既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(a) 大遊行<br />\n<br />\n有巴打覺得要整番場大遊行黎搞番起個勢<br />\n大遊行相信可以做到整合番己方既效果<br />\n因為呢排大家咁多唔同意見 整番場和理非遊行<br />\n可以吸納番多D人投入運動 始終越多人支持既運動先可以越持久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(例如之前既 遊行集會+deadline+升級 既策略)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">但遊行必須要多人 文宣同事前宣傳一定要做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則得幾萬條友出黎就變晒示弱 反而令自己處於更弱勢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(b) 行動目的<br />\n<br />\n當然每一次行動都係要求政府正面回應五大訴求<br />\n但係之前既行動相對地都有明確既目標 完成後就散場<br />\n(無論係即時傾出黎定事前度好) <br />\n例如6.12阻止二讀, 6.21圍警總撚狗, 7.1重奪立會, 7.21中聯辦<br />\n近期有D行動相對效果就較弱同好傷 <br />\n(e.g. 7.28算重傷, 40幾個手足被拉)<br />\n<br />\n如果之後再搞活動既話 呢樣野值得大家諗下<br />\n所以有人會覺得討論機場 禮賓府 之類既地方<br />\n唔係我驚大家就係無乜目的咁周圍行 <br />\n然後就等狗黎+避難無限loop<br />\n要記住班狗已經不顧任何面子同規則<br />\n無論地鐵站商場個D佢會照入照開槍<br />\n目的就係佢地口中既「止暴制亂」<br />\n<br />\n假如我地要針對五大訴求同追究7.21恐襲<br />\n就要做番D有可能達到令運動向前既行動<br />\n不停打遊擊好容易墮入為打而打既陷阱<br />\n我地平時屌泛民行禮如儀 同時要警惕自己唔好做相同既野<br />\n學天琦咁講:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？」</span><br />\n<br />\n另外想講少少 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家記住對同路人/旁觀者要禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n佢地冇做咩攻擊你既行為個陣 唔需要亂咁起鋼<br />\n我唔去揣測呢D野係咪鬼做 總之大家做好自己<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Politics is perception</span> 觀感呢樣野好現實<br />\n就算你係扮 都要扮比全世界睇 <br />\n當然做好自己亦都可以令自己進步<br />\n同時令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己 改變想法<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊討論下<br />\n我會幫大家sum番重點 等大家易D閱讀<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲繼續努力 <ins>政府已經無視所有社會規則黎出牌<br />\n即係佢地已經無咩有說服力既招數 唯有霸王硬上弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要堅持信念我地一定會贏<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\nps放核彈都唔割!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12852e6c05f95d73065a9ef23a0f55b1fab453db","tid":1447042,"uid":259622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/z57whys0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fz57whys0&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d24928ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/z57whys0</a><br />\n狗扮示威者射催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae6c4ba34d7bab1eba1b821721156c70d8d08ba","tid":1447042,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12852e6c05f95d73065a9ef23a0f55b1fab453db","tid":1447042,"uid":259622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/z57whys0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fz57whys0&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=d24928ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/z57whys0</a><br />\n狗扮示威者射催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"文宣巴打今晚大把料做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096b64f8c6dd0db5d08b3110839d238974e94567","tid":1447042,"uid":2617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"},{"pid":"2135b5f93d5f50f88aba9167a725aa25b5690e4f","tid":1447042,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5963a63f8c54f442304adf3c83b72600c72e30d","tid":1447042,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2135b5f93d5f50f88aba9167a725aa25b5690e4f","tid":1447042,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論下 我見咁多戰術Post <br />\n純粹想集中下 我可以幫大家做總結 <br />\n比大家參考下 希望有用"},{"pid":"8088fddc3b3962a1622ffa208b8fa96f7302d744","tid":1447042,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score